# ğŸ“ Task Manager Web App

A clean, modern, feature-rich To-Do & Task Manager Web App built using only vanilla JavaScript, HTML5, CSS3, and Bootstrap 5 â€” no frameworks, no libraries.  
All UI and logic are fully JS-driven, even the HTML structure is dynamically generated.

