## ğŸš€ Features

### âœ… Add, Edit & Delete Tasks
- Add tasks with:
  - Unique ID
  - Name
  - Description
  - Date & Time
  - (Optional) Image URL
- Edit tasks inline.
- Soft-delete (mark for deletion), with batch delete capability.

### ğŸ—“ï¸ Smart Date & Time Integration
- Schedule tasks with specific date and time.
- Each task auto-generates a UNIX timestamp.
- Designed for calendar integrations and automation tools.

### ğŸ“¡ AutoRemote Integration (Task Automation)
- On "Save", each task with a date/time sends a message to [AutoRemote](https://joaoapps.com/autoremote/) with:
  - Timestamp
  - Task name
  - Description
- Use to trigger reminders or automate notifications on Android phones.

### ğŸ’¾ Local Storage Support
- All tasks are saved to your browserâ€™s localStorage.
- Load previously saved tasks anytime.
- Fully offline-capable â€” no backend required.

### ğŸŒ Load from Server (Optional)
- Fetch tasks from a local `tasks.json` file.
- Useful for demos or mock APIs.

### ğŸ’¡ Smart UI & UX
- Live task counters:
  - Total Tasks
  - Marked for Deletion
  - Remaining Tasks
- Live photo previews (if image URL provided).
- Responsive for mobile/tablet.
- Animated buttons and click effects.

### ğŸŒˆ Modern UI Design
- Built with Bootstrap 5
- Custom CSS for:
  - Animated buttons
  - Icon-based editing/deleting
  - Responsive layout

---

## ğŸ” AutoRemote Key Configuration

To enable AutoRemote:
1. Get your AutoRemote key from [here](https://joaoapps.com/autoremote/).
2. Replace the `key=` value inside the `sendToAutoRemote()` function in the source code with your own key.

Thatâ€™s it! Saving tasks will now trigger remote messages.

