## ğŸ› ï¸ Installation & Usage

1. **Clone the repository:**
   ```sh
   git clone https://github.com/Chandan98S/To-Do-Application.git
   cd To-Do-Application
   ```
2. **Open `index.html` in your browser.**
   - No server or build steps needed; everything runs in the browser.
3. **(Optional) To enable server loading:**
   - Place a valid `tasks.json` in your project root and serve with [Live Server](https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=ritwickdey.LiveServer) or any static server.

